2026-04-14 17:10:57,608 - DEBUG - Remote response: status=200 | data={"value":"{\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Woolworths Natural Greek Style Yoghurt  1kg\",\"image\":\"https://cdn0.woolworths.media/content/wowproductimages/large/571487.jpg\",\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":4.56,\"ratingCount\":1231},\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Woolworths\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"potentialAction\":{\"@type\":\"BuyAction\"},\"url\":\"https://www.woolworths.com.au/shop/productdetails/571487/woolworths-natural-greek-style-yoghurt\",\"availability\":\"http://schema.org/InStock\",\"price\":3.8,\"priceCurrency\":\"AUD\",\"priceSpecification\":{\"@type\":\"UnitPriceSpecification\",\"priceCurrency\":\"AUD\",\"priceType\":\"https://schema.org/ListPrice\",\"price\":0.38,\"unitText\":\"1kg\"},\"seller\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Woolworths\"}},\"review\":[{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"description\":\"Value and quality. I was surprised how good this brand is. It is just thick enough, really creamy, and little bit tangy, and great in sweet and savoury dishes.\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"aupanda\"},\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-11T06:01:00.0000000+00:00\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"bestRating\":5,\"ratingValue\":5,\"worstRating\":1}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"description\":\"Woolworths Natural Greek Style Yoghurt 1kg. Creamy and mildly tangy, this yoghurt works well for breakfast or cooking. The texture is fairly smooth, though not as thick as premium Greek yoghurts. Flavour is simple and slightly plain. Good value for the size, but don’t expect a rich, indulgent experience.\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"imsorryto\"},\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-04T08:02:00.0000000+00:00\",\"reviewRating\":{\"@type\":\"Rating\",\"bestRating\":5,\"ratingValue\":3,\"worstRating\":1}},{\"@type\":\"Review\",\"description\":\"Decent Greek yogurt! I loved this sample, such a versatile product to use. 